subproject.description:
-To extend the survival rate and restore the quality of life of individuals living with HIV/AIDS in Haiti;
 To slow down the spread of HIV/AIDS in Haiti; and
 To empower sexually active Haitians to make informed choices and to adopt behaviors that protect their health, reduce their risk and vulnerability to HIV/AIDS and other Sexually Transmitted Infections (STIs), and contribute to the elimination of stigmatization of, and discrimination against, those infected and affected by HIV/AIDS.
